704386f-a.title: Brooklyn: Flushing Avenue - Elliott Place (North)
704386f-a.text:
Flushing Avenue, south side, west from N. Elliott Flace.
At the left foreground between N. Elliott Place and St. Edwards
SStreet are some old buildings soon to be demolished. Beyond
St. EdNards Street is a city park.
August 25, 1938.
P.L. Sperr
